<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 12 December 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.232</title>
<h1>12 December 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.232</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>brdcast@mx.jamestown.org</i>)<br>
