<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 6 December 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.228</title>
<h1>6 December 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.228</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>brdcast@mx.jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 6 Dec 1996 09:06:31 -0500</i>
<p>
