<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 21 November 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.219</title>
<h1>21 November 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.219</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>brdcast@mx.jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 21 Nov 1996 10:16:26 -0500</i>
