<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 20 November 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.218</title>
<h1>20 November 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.218</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>brdcast@mx.jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 20 Nov 1996 09:47:57 -0500</i>
<p>
