<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 12 November 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.212</title>
<h1>12 November 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.212</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>brdcast@mx.jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 12 Nov 1996 09:56:30 -0500</i>
<p>
