<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 11 November 1996 Monitor - Vol. II, No. 211</title>
<h1>11 November 1996 Monitor - Vol. II, No. 211</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>eckert@mx.jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 11 Nov 1996 10:19:37 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#42">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#42">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#42">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#42">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0043.html">Jamestown Foundation: "12 November 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.212"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0041.html">Jamestown Foundation: "8 November 1996 Monitor - Vol. II, No. 210"</a>
