<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 7 November 1996 Monitor - Vol. II, No. 209</title>
<h1>7 November 1996 Monitor - Vol. II, No. 209</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>eckert@mx.jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 07 Nov 1996 11:11:21 -0500</i>
<p>
