<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 21 October 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.196</title>
<h1>21 October 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.196</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>brdcast@jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 21 Oct 1996 09:31:08 -0400</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#22">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#22">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#22">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#22">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0023.html">Jamestown Foundation: "22 October 1996 Monitor - Vol.II, No.197"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0021.html">Jamestown Foundation: "18 October 1996 Fortnight In Review - Vol. I, No. 8"</a>
