<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 18 October 1996 - Monitor Vol. II, No. 195</title>
<h1>18 October 1996 - Monitor Vol. II, No. 195</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>brdcast@jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 18 Oct 1996 09:34:40 -0400</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#20">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#20">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#20">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#20">[ author ]</a>
