<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 16 October 1996 - Monitor Vol. II, No. 193</title>
<h1>16 October 1996 - Monitor Vol. II, No. 193</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>brdcast@jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 16 Oct 1996 09:48:12 -0400</i>
<p>
