<title>The Monitor: A Publication of the Jamestown Foundation: 9 October 1996 - Monitor Vol. II, No. 188</title>
<h1>9 October 1996 - Monitor Vol. II, No. 188</h1>
Jamestown Foundation (<i>brdcast@jamestown.org</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 9 Oct 1996 09:40:00 -0400</i>
<p>
