<li> <a href="0037.html"><b>OMRI--10OCT 1996--FRENCH FOREIGN MINISTER IN ARMENIA</b></a> <a name="37"><i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i></a>
<li> <a href="0036.html"><b>OMRI--9 OCT 1996--ARMENIAN GOVERNMENT ACCUSED OF HUMAN RIGHT</b></a> <a name="36"><i>kkhalmatov@sorosny.org</i></a>
<li> <a href="0035.html"><b>OMRI--8 OCT 1996--NEW ROUND OF KARABAKH DIPLOMACY</b></a> <a name="35"><i>kkhalmatov@sorosny.org</i></a>
<li> <a href="0034.html"><b>OMRI - Oct 9 1996 -- ARM. GOV'T ACCUSED OF RIGHTS VIOLATIONS</b></a> <a name="34"><i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i></a>
